\par }{\b\f0\insrsid12540821\charrsid1315154 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Al- Ghazali:}{\f0\insrsid12540821\charrsid1315154 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
 "Lying is the mother of all great sins. If a person is known as a liar, no trust in his words remains, he loses prestige, and his opinions be\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
come worthless. If you want to understand the ugliness of lying, look at the ugliness of the lies of others and see the extent to which your soul feels hatred. Note how much the liar is held in contempt and how ugly you will find the lie that is told..."}
