\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 If for the truth to be uttered it is damaging, it resigns its place to silence; lies have no place, even if they have some use. 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Everything you say should be true, all your pronouncements right, but you have no right to say \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 all that is true. 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 . . . See the good side of things;you will have good thoughts. Know things to be good and think of them as good; you will find the pleasure in life.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 In life, hope and thinking favorably of things are life itself. While to think the worst\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  is despair, the destroyer of happiness and slayer of life."}{\f0\up6\insrsid12540821\charrsid1315154 
