\par }{\b\f0\insrsid12540821\charrsid1315154 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Mehmed Zahid Kotku:}{\f0\insrsid12540821\charrsid1315154 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
 "There are three signs of a hypocrite: When he speaks, he lies, does not keep his word, and is treacherous with what is entrusted to him." If these three easily recognizab\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
le ugly forms of behavior are to be found in the same person, we do not hesitate to brand him a hypocrite right away.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 There are two aspects of hypocrisy. One relates to one's acts, the other to one's belief, which is the most serious one. The sign of both \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 is the three types of behavior mentioned above.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Lying is strongly condemned by\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
 every society, every people, and every individual. In Turkish, we say: 'The liar's candle burns until evening prayers.' Light is a night-time need for people. If you lie, this means you are deprived of the light that you need at night and remain all nigh
